<div class="box en">💡 <strong>What to watch now:</strong> (1) whether Abraxas's roughly $440 million in seven-day inflows is a one-off or the start of a sustained pattern over coming weeks; (2) whether Aave's ether utilization rate and borrowing costs move meaningfully lower as a result of this flow; and (3) what happens to the validator exit queue and the stETH peg if a large wallet reverses direction the way the Justin Sun-linked withdrawal did.</div>
